    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It honestly breaks my heart a little to list this beauty, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed with love every single weekend. It still has that wonderful new-car scent and drives as smooth as the day it left the lot. There\u2019s a tiny, barely-there mark on the rim from a stray pebble, but you\u2019d honestly need a magnifying glass to find it! This is a pristine gem that\u2019s ready for the open road. Swing by, let's grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this ride is so special.",
